descp2: A `Tensor` of type `float32`. The minimum value of the quantization range. This value may be adjusted by the op depending on other parameters. The adjusted value is written to `output_min`. If the `axis` attribute is specified, this must be a 1-D tensor whose size matches the `axis` dimension of the input and output tensors.
